    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n5126" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κατα - φθίω</span></b> , fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-φθί̄σει</span>, mid. aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κατέφθιτο</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">καταφθίσθαι</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-φθίμενος</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">destroy</span>, mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">perish,
